Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>
#Build-Depends: bash, imagemagick, debhelper (>= 7)
Build-Depends: bash, debhelper (>= 7)
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Homepage: http://launchpad.net/semplice

Package: semplice-artwork
Architecture: all
Depends: semplice-artwork-wallpapers, semplice-artwork-theme, semplice-artwork-gdm3
Description: Semplice System Artwork metapackage
 This package depends on the default artwork
 of the Semplice Project.

Package: semplice-artwork-wallpapers
Architecture: all
Description: Semplice System default Wallpapers
 This package contains the Semplice System default wallpapers.
 Actually, it contains:
  * pulse: the default wallpaper.

Package: semplice-artwork-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: gnome-brave-icon-theme, gtk2-engines-equinox (>= 1.40), gnome-themes-standard, gtk2-engines-pixbuf, ttf-droid
Recommends: dmz-cursor-theme
Description: Semplice System GTK+ and openbox themes
 This package contains:
  * SempliceDusk: dark, default theme. Based on Equinox Evolution Dusk.
    The Openbox theme is based on "Clearlooks" theme.
    The GTK3 theme is based on "Adwaita" theme.
  * Semplice: light, old default. Based on Equinox.
    The Openbox theme is based on "Elementary" theme.

Package: semplice-artwork-gdm3
Architecture: all
Depends: gnome-icon-theme-symbolic
Recommends: gdm3
Description: Semplice System GDM3 artwork
 This package contains the artwork needed by GDM3.
